    "settings.language-servers.info": {
      "comment": "String 'CodeEdit makes use of the Mason Registry for language server installation. To install a package, CodeEdit uses the package manager directed by the Mason Registry, and installs a copy of the language server in Application Support.\\n\\nLanguage server installation is still experimental, there may be bugs and expect this flow to change over time.' appears at line 68 in LanguageServersView.swift within the string property. This is informational text explaining to users how the language server",
